comments:
For me, the alien words were quite strange/unfamiliar to begin with and it was quite difficult to grasp the them let alone memorize. however, I tried to make-out usual or familiar terms out of these unusual words in order to remember the alien objects as well. I did not find the study easy and I might say it was quite complex for me.
I would love to try it again sometime though, I think I can do better lol. 
I have found this survey to be quite interesting.
